We've been after
this... family heirloom of Pope's,

14:13.978 --> 14:15.688
which is why we were gone.

14:15.688 --> 14:17.690
And we ended up losing it,

14:17.690 --> 14:22.653
and unbelievably there might be a chance
that, um, we could get it back tonight.

14:23.237 --> 14:24.238
In Wilmington.

14:24.780 --> 14:26.115
- Okay.
- It's crazy.

14:26.115 --> 14:27.825
Okay. How... how can I help?

14:27.825 --> 14:30.619
- No, I can't ask you to do that.
- No, seriously.

14:30.619 --> 14:35.416
Topper, I feel like if I ask you,
just, like, the person that you are...

14:35.416 --> 14:39.086
- What do you mean, "the person I am"?
- No, I didn't mean it like that.

14:39.086 --> 14:41.797
I guess I mean
you're such a giver, Topper.

14:41.797 --> 14:44.466
You're just such a helper,
and I feel like if I ask you--

14:44.466 --> 14:46.552
Sarah, that's just... that's just who I am.

14:46.552 --> 14:49.179
That's just the way I was raised.

14:49.972 --> 14:53.225
And anyway, remember when I said
I would do literally anything for you?

14:53.225 --> 14:54.351
Remember that?

14:54.935 --> 14:55.895
Yeah.

14:57.271 --> 14:58.439
I meant it.

14:58.439 --> 15:01.150
Unlike some people
who will just say whatever to get you

15:01.150 --> 15:02.943
to go along with whatever they want.

15:02.943 --> 15:06.071
I'm not that person, okay?
When I say something, I mean it.

15:06.071 --> 15:07.364
I need your truck.

15:09.491 --> 15:11.785
-  My dad's truck?
- Four wheels.

15:13.120 --> 15:15.456
Oh my God. He would literally kill me.

15:15.456 --> 15:19.335
- He's super anal about it.
- So are we. We're super anal.

15:19.335 --> 15:22.463
We, like... we... we...
we'll take such good care of it.

15:22.463 --> 15:25.424
You put me in a tough spot.
I know I said I'd do anything but...

15:26.216 --> 15:28.052
I'm so sorry about everything.

15:31.472 --> 15:34.934
I totally understand.
You have no reason to help us.

15:34.934 --> 15:37.519
Actually, you have
all the reasons not to help us.

15:38.896 --> 15:40.731
Why do I feel like I'll regret this?

15:54.244 --> 15:56.580
Figured out a way
to get in without a key card?

15:56.580 --> 15:57.665
No plan yet.

15:58.332 --> 16:02.169
Just got to wait for the night to settle.
Less people around, the better.

16:03.212 --> 16:04.630
We'll wait till the witching hour

16:04.630 --> 16:06.966
then get down
to some serious cat burgling.

16:07.925 --> 16:08.968
Grit?

16:10.010 --> 16:11.011
I'm good.

16:11.637 --> 16:12.763
Ah, that a boy.

16:16.934 --> 16:19.728
You know what is true, though?
All faults aside,

16:20.312 --> 16:22.314
it is nice to be back together with you.

16:24.650 --> 16:25.609
Yeah, it is.

16:28.237 --> 16:29.071
It sure is.

16:31.949 --> 16:33.200
Oh, three o'clock, eh?

16:40.791 --> 16:43.836
I think I might've bought
a racehorse at that silent auction.

16:43.836 --> 16:46.005
-  What?

16:46.005 --> 16:48.507
I thought it was a horse ranch.

16:48.507 --> 16:50.676
You know, I'm on the board of directors.

16:50.676 --> 16:53.095
Being on the board has its privileges.

16:53.095 --> 16:55.597
This is it.
This could be our chance.

16:55.597 --> 16:57.141
Oh my God. Really?

16:57.725 --> 16:58.642
Let's go.

17:01.478 --> 17:03.772
My God,
are we allowed to go in here?

17:03.772 --> 17:05.607
-  Hell of a dress, lady.
- Thank you.

17:05.607 --> 17:07.609
I'm about to trip all over it.

17:07.609 --> 17:11.822
About 5% of the collection is ever
on display at any given time.

17:11.822 --> 17:13.615
- The rest of it, it's in here.
- What's--

17:13.615 --> 17:15.909
Really? Are we allowed to? Oh my God.

17:15.909 --> 17:17.745
-  Let's go.

17:22.416 --> 17:24.418
Nice catch!

17:31.842 --> 17:34.053
 Well,
there's like 1,000 trains here.

17:34.053 --> 17:36.889
Well, we know it's car 750X
on the track to Raleigh.

17:36.889 --> 17:38.891
Yeah, so now we just gotta find it.

17:38.891 --> 17:40.350
Well, news flash.

17:40.350 --> 17:43.854
We're not getting out
of here unnoticed with a giant cross.

17:43.854 --> 17:46.899
We won't have to. We can nab it
somewhere further in the country.

17:46.899 --> 17:48.942
Just gotta figure out
how to stop the train.

17:49.860 --> 17:50.694
Right.

17:51.278 --> 17:53.655
