20:42.991 --> 20:45.786
It's gonna be all right.
It's gonna be all right.

20:53.335 --> 20:54.544
7-2-6.

20:55.545 --> 20:56.463
Hold on.

20:57.923 --> 20:59.258
750X, baby.

