22:37.064 --> 22:38.398
What's the point?

22:38.398 --> 22:40.484
- That's the last of the Trinity boxes.
- Shh.

22:41.318 --> 22:42.778
It's over.

22:45.072 --> 22:46.323
It's over.

22:48.575 --> 22:50.369
It was a long shot, anyway.

22:58.001 --> 23:00.087
Goddamn it.

23:08.428 --> 23:11.306
There's so much disappointments,
