31:12.161 --> 31:14.747
- Right here.

31:16.291 --> 31:19.335
-  How's it looking?
-  Still searching.

31:24.257 --> 31:25.800
That's good. That's good right there.

31:27.594 --> 31:28.595
- You see it?
-  Hey.

31:28.595 --> 31:30.513
- What?
-  This one says Cameron.

31:30.513 --> 31:32.682
- It might be this one.
