a thousand paint jobs after we do this.

31:42.650 --> 31:45.194
-  This thing right here?
- Just help us spot it.

31:45.194 --> 31:46.446
I got you.

31:46.446 --> 31:48.031
- All right.
-  Topper, help me!

31:48.031 --> 31:51.367
- Help me with the door.
-  Just push it this way.

31:51.367 --> 31:53.453
- My dad's gonna kill me.
-  Guide it.

31:56.039 --> 31:57.749
- Shit.
-  That can't be good.

31:57.749 --> 32:00.418
-  Quick!
-  Hurry up, let's go!

32:00.418 --> 32:03.338
- What is in here? It's stuck. Go back.

32:03.922 --> 32:06.382
- Don't mess up the cross!
- Don't mess up the truck!

32:06.966 --> 32:08.676
All right, all good to go.

32:08.676 --> 32:10.970
- The train's starting.
- We gotta go get them.

32:10.970 --> 32:13.139
- There goes the plan. We gotta help them.
- Come on.

32:14.432 --> 32:16.351
- Come on.

32:18.186 --> 32:20.813
